# Migrate Command + Field Rename Implementation Plan

> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.

**Goal:** Rename `gist_id`→remove and `asc_page`→`sp_docs_page` across all SDK repos and harness code; add `gendocs --clean`; add `DOC_PAGE_STALE_IMPORT` audit finding; add `migrate` command that replaces hardcoded `<CodeGroup>` blocks with generated snippet imports.

**Architecture:** Scanner gains `SpDocsPage` field with backward-compat parsing of old `asc_page:` key. New `internal/matcher` package builds a reverse index from snippet groups to doc page paths. `DOC_PAGE_STALE_IMPORT` audit finding detects doc pages not yet using their generated snippets. `migrate` command rewrites those doc pages: adds `import` at top + replaces `<CodeGroup>` block with `<ComponentName />`.

**Tech Stack:** Go 1.22, testify, existing harness packages (scanner, differ, report, docgen, pages, fixer)

